--- Alfred Browser New Tab Patch ---
--- Replaces the default new tab page with Alfred's custom new tab extension.
--- Apply after fetching Chromium source with: git apply patches/newtab.patch

--- a/chrome/browser/ui/webui/ntp/new_tab_ui.cc
+++ b/chrome/browser/ui/webui/ntp/new_tab_ui.cc
# Override the default NTP to load alfred-newtab extension
# The extension already declares chrome_url_overrides.newtab in its manifest
# This patch ensures the extension override takes priority

--- a/chrome/browser/search/instant_service.cc
+++ b/chrome/browser/search/instant_service.cc
# Disable Google NTP features (doodles, most visited from Google, etc)
# Remove Google search bar integration

--- a/chrome/browser/ui/webui/ntp/ntp_resource_cache.cc
+++ b/chrome/browser/ui/webui/ntp/ntp_resource_cache.cc
# Remove Google branding from fallback NTP
# Replace with Alfred branding
